kiwix-tools
------------------------------------------
The Kiwix tools is a collection of Kiwix related command line tools.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.5.1-1
  libgcc1-11.4.0-1
  libkiwix13-13.1.0-1bl1
  libstdc++6-11.4.0-1
  libzim9-9.1.0-1bl1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.42-1
  cygport-0.36.8-1
  gcc-core-11.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-11.4.0-1
  libkiwix-devel-13.1.0-1bl1
  libzim-devel-9.1.0-1bl1
  meson-1.2.3-1
  ninja-1.11.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/kiwix/kiwix-tools

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/kiwix/kiwix-tools/archive/refs/tags/3.7.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack kiwix-tools-3.7.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./kiwix-tools-3.7.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/kiwix-tools-3.7.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/kiwix-tools-3.7.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(kiwix-tools)
  /usr/bin/kiwix-manage.exe
  /usr/bin/kiwix-search.exe
  /usr/bin/kiwix-serve.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/kiwix-tools.README
  /usr/share/doc/kiwix-tools/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/kiwix-tools/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/kiwix-tools/Changelog
  /usr/share/doc/kiwix-tools/README.md
  /usr/share/man/fr/man1/kiwix-manage.1.gz
  /usr/share/man/fr/man1/kiwix-serve.1.gz
  /usr/share/man/man1/kiwix-manage.1.gz
  /usr/share/man/man1/kiwix-search.1.gz
  /usr/share/man/man1/kiwix-serve.1.gz

